msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>That's great to hear, you should get some rest. Tomorrow will be your first day. I'll call you at around 6 am, so make sure to be up by then.</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick : </><Speech>Content de l'entendre, tu devrais te reposer. Demain sera ton premier jour. Je t'appellerai vers 6 h du matin, alors assure-toi d'être debout d'ici là.</>"

